{"tid":997309,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南華早報突發：孫楊或被罰終身停賽","createTime":"2019-01-27T05:16:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T06:16:36.000Z","uid":5195,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"82010a4e45ce7f28c810ace7772569ba8f817811","tid":997309,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T05:16:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/sport/article/2183798/chinas-sun-yang-faces-life-ban-smashing-blood-samples-front-anti-doping\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fsport%2Farticle%2F2183798%2Fchinas-sun-yang-faces-life-ban-smashing-blood-samples-front-anti-doping&d=%2BFEzSYEz1bTH5AdSBpjkdKS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=daa8f92a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/sport/article/2183798/chinas-sun-yang-faces-life-ban-smashing-blood-samples-front-anti-doping</a><br />\n<br />\nChina&rsquo;s greatest swimmer faces a lifetime ban from the pool, according to a remarkable report from The Sunday Times.<br />\n<br />\nSun Yang, who has been called the &ldquo;greatest freestyle swimmer of all time&rdquo; on account of being the only man to win Olympic gold in the 200m, 400m, and 1,500m freestyle, has been accused of taking matters into his own hands with drug testers at an out-of-competition test at his home.<br />\n<br />\nThe report alleges Sun and his team destroyed blood samples in front of anti-doping testers, with a hammer used to smash a vial containing the swimmer&rsquo;s blood at the demand of the swimmer&rsquo;s mother."},{"pid":"6a1f117c62814c417f6c93447abe9346d543b037","tid":997309,"uid":13897,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T05:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fc8b393511e114b1627bfa14897a9974f06492c","tid":997309,"uid":103156,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T05:26:33.000Z","msg":"China&rsquo;s greatest <span style=\"color: red;\">CHEATING</span> swimmer faces a lifetime ban from the pool, according to a remarkable report from The Sunday Times."},{"pid":"06eec9a6332e4938933fb29a35bca26aa7d31440","tid":997309,"uid":2419,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T05:28:39.000Z","msg":"紫尿狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該要褫奪埋之前d獎牌啦"},{"pid":"b1e8573b338089d5ab345cab65a00746c2afb01b","tid":997309,"uid":61882,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T05:29:28.000Z","msg":"尿紫楊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n英國權威媒體&ldquo;泰晤士報&rdquo;今天發布報導，稱在去年年底孫楊與反興奮劑檢測員發生衝突，其保安利用錘子砸碎裝有檢測血液的密封瓶子，此舉或將導致孫楊將面臨終生禁賽。<br />\n<br />\n據&ldquo;泰晤士報&rdquo;報導測試人員來到了孫楊在浙江省的家中，並因為他不在家而被要求在外面等了將近一個小時。<br />\n<br />\n孫楊於晚上11點到家，雖然一位護士在附近的俱樂部採集了血樣，但孫楊對檢測人員身份質疑，聲稱這不足以證明其是測試團隊的正式成員。<br />\n<br />\n隨著爭議的升級，孫楊母親楊明聲稱她有警察聯繫人，他們會檢查在場的人。據稱，孫楊的醫生巴震於凌晨1點到達並詢問了護士取血的資格目擊者。稱，楊明指使一名保安拿起一把錘子來摧毀裝著血的樣瓶。<br />\n<br />\n為了尋求支持，巴震隨後聯繫了浙江反興奮劑中心負責人韓照歧，韓照歧告訴國際泳聯興奮劑小組聽證會，護士的文書工作不充分。小組接受了他的話，在報告中稱他們&ldquo;永遠不會知道&ldquo;事實的真相。在1月3日，該小組還是站在運動員這一邊。<br />\n<br />\n當天，主要測試人員多次打電話給位於瑞典的國際興奮劑檢測與管理中心總部尋求建議，力圖完成對樣本的蒐集，其中一通電話中可以清晰的聽到現場的爭執聲。據悉，孫楊和保安人員用錘子砸碎了小瓶，測試人員拒絕了孫楊一行人提出的交出第二個小瓶的要求。孫楊搶走了檢測人員的報告書並撕毀。隨後測試人員告訴孫楊一行人，他們的行為會違反反興奮劑準則終於。在凌晨3點15左右，爭執就此停息，而楊明收集了所有測試材料殘餘並離開。<br />\n<br />\n目前，國際泳聯與國際興奮劑檢測與管理中心均未做出回應。"},{"pid":"9b2f555b23f24da1e6fdb644e59b213fc15ae6d0","tid":997309,"uid":35648,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T05:30:18.000Z","msg":"The report alleges Sun and his team destroyed blood samples in front of anti-doping testers, with a hammer used to smash a vial containing the swimmer&rsquo;s blood at the demand of the swimmer&rsquo;s mother.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果係真，唔停賽都俾人笑到唔敢參加啦，媽媽叫我鎚爛啲血液樣本<br />\n定係想對手見到佢個樣笑到游唔到棄權呀"},{"pid":"efde2fb845e2baba5befa43d031e7fef6962f8bc","tid":997309,"uid":75570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T05:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66443890c36cbf4f2f06c4143cf4dc0cbbbf0843","tid":997309,"uid":11148,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T05:33:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YvHu9TT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYvHu9TT.jpg&h=15dc5857&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6LPhzky.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6LPhzky.jpg&h=7bb33e68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ycHfk0z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FycHfk0z.jpg&h=16166135&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zeqXzkA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzeqXzkA.jpg&h=d9c28dea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Lhu9TV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Lhu9TV.jpg&h=633c6184&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src